My name is Hillary Nnamdi Evans and I am a full-stack Web Application Developer and Software Developer currently pursuing a Bachelor of Technology in Computer Science at Federal University of Technology Owerri,Nigeria.My primary focus and inspiration as regards my studies is Software Development. I also love to study Human-Computer Interfacing and the psychology of human computer interaction. I am both driven and self-motivated, and I am constantly experimenting with new technologies and techniques. I am very passionate about Web/Software Development, and I aim at becoming a better developer.My Pastimes are Playing video games,Watching comic movies.Lest I forget,I am an ardent christian!
I have been studying web/Software development since 2010 and I develop in Ruby(Rails Framework),C#,PHP, though I primarily use Rails. I am experienced in both front and back-end development, and I am proficient in HTML CSS/CSS3, SASS, XML, JavaScript, jQuery, AJAX, and SQL/MySQL/ORACLE, to name a few. I am also proficient in non-web-based languages, including but not limited to C# for desktop application etc. I have also worked on some smaller Ruby and PHP projects, and have used the languages to create one-time use tools for data processing and similar purposes.
